summary: GoT themed ask game cus i need someone to scream about GoT with
body:
GoT themed ask game cus i need someone to scream about GoT with

send a number to my inbox and i’ll answer the question!

  1. how did you get into got? who, if anyone, introduced you to it?
  2. books or tv series, and why?
  3. who do you WANT to die?
  4. who do you think will REALISTICALLY die?
  5. would jon or daenerys serve as a better protector of the realm? will their relationship survive their individual claims to the iron throne?
  6. what are your thoughts on the legend of azor ahai? who do you think is azor ahai come again, if there is one?
  7. should the living triumph, what do you think will happen to the house-based society?
  8. send a ship and i’ll rate it with justification: if one or both of them dies i’m dying with them | ABSOLUTELY ADORABLE | cute! | alright | eh | not really… | god no | GOD NO | they’re literally related
  9. what do you think will really result in the most deaths? (army of the dead, inter-house conflict, starvation, epidemic etc etc)
  10. which subplots are you tired of?
  11. which subplots do you want to see more of?
  12. send one or more subtextual themes and i’ll discuss them: family | unity vs distrust | life vs death | natural vs unnatural | legend vs reality | prophecy | gender | racism and xenophobia | loyalty | religion | fire and ice (duh) | past feuds and conflict | class and house warfare | any other you can think of!
  13. do you think any other characters will come to help, or are the current winterfell inhabitants on their own?
  14. who are some characters who have died but deserved to have lasted longer?
  15. who are some characters who are still alive but do not really deserve to have lasted this long?
  16. were there any events that you predicted would happen before they actually happened?
  17. which fan theories do you follow and believe?
  18. which fan theories do you think are absolutely bananas?
  19. do you think jaime will ever return to king’s landing?
  20. do you think sansa and the lords of the north are right to be distrustful of daenerys, or are they just making things more difficult for everyone else?
  21. which characters do you think will retain their grudges, and which will let bygones be bygones?
  22. a lot of people are gonna be confined in one (comparably) small fortress for a long siege and longer winter. which characters can you see getting together or breaking up?
  23. how would you judge the show’s characters, plot and worldbuilding?
  24. what do you like most about game of thrones? what do you like least?
  25. finally, ask anything you like!

summary:
1. "she's the smartest person I know " 
ARYA TELLING IT LIKE IT IS 
After last season, I love the fact that my Stark sisters are...
body:
1. “she’s the smartest person I know ”

ARYA TELLING IT LIKE IT IS

After last season, I love the fact that my Stark sisters are sticking together.

2.With that,

“I’m part of her family too”

“don’t forget that”

OH HE GONNA FORGET THAT

FORESHADOWING AT IT’S FINEST

3.SPEAKING OF FORESHADOWING

Varys going “Nothing lasts”

It shows.

4.“What do they(dragons) even eat?”

“Whatever they want”

did Danny girl just tell everyone she can’t control her children also home girl that ain’t something to be proud of.

5.“Your sister doesn’t like me ”

“If she can’t respect me….”

HONESTLY HOW FUCKING DARE YOU

6.“I thought you were the cleverest man in the world”

Tyrion bb pls come to your senses I love you and miss you being smart.

7.THE ENTIRETY OF ARYA AND GENDRY OHMYGOD

I’VE MISSED THEM SO MUCH.

8.“Stay back! He’s got blue eyes”

“I’VE ALWAYS HAD BLUE EYES”

Peak comedy

9. Loved the parallel of the last scene with Jamie and bran with the last scene of season 1 episode 1

10.Bottom line , will die for the Stark girls

11.Also bottom line, Danny’s resort to violence was efficient and smart when she lived with rapists and slave masters

She’s in the civilized world now

She just can’t burn everyone who doesn’t agree with her.

12. Also someone please give Cersei some elephants
